THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

This repository integrates, but does not redistribute, the following:

  * SALMONN (bytedance/SALMONN) — Apache-2.0. Fetched by scripts/setup_salmonn.sh.
  * Vicuna-7B-v1.5 (lmsys)      — subject to Meta's LLaMA license terms.
  * Whisper-large-v2 (OpenAI)   — MIT.
  * BEATs (Microsoft)           — MIT.
  * NISQA (gabrielmittag/NISQA) — MIT. Fetched by scripts/setup_salmonn.sh.

Datasets (LibriTTS-R, MUSAN, measured RIRs, VoiceBank-DEMAND) are NOT redistributed here;
you must obtain them from their sources under their own licenses. See REPRODUCING.md.

The published Plan B checkpoints contain only the ~30 M trained parameters (Q-Former,
speech->LLaMA projection, and the Vicuna LoRA adapter) — no base-model weights.
